A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: There are moments of star wars fun to be had for sure  but overall this film was very confusing. The plot felt muddled and some of them felt unnecessary and contrived. There were a couple of cringeworthy moments too! Overall it felt bizarre and not like a star wars movie at all. After waiting 30 years it was very disappointing. I hope Disney can produce something more worthy in the future.
